description:
The Google app keeps you in the know about things that matter to you. Find quick answers, explore your interests and stay up to date with Discover.

• Use your camera to identify what you're looking at – whether that's a colourful butterfly, a spiky plant or anything else you're curious about.
• Translate over 100 languages on things like street signs, menus and any other words you can point your camera at.
• See something you like? Use your camera to find out where you can buy it.
• Refine your camera searches by adding words – whether you want those shoes but in 'blue', or want to learn how to 'repair' that broken piece on your bicycle.
• Search by singing, even when you've forgotten the lyrics. Hum a song into the Google app to find out what it is.
• Use your camera for homework help. With step-by-step guides and videos, you can learn ways to solve maths, chemistry, biology and physics problems.


Get personalised updates in Discover:
• Stay in the know about topics that interest you.
• Start your morning with weather and top news.
• Get real-time updates on sports, films and events.
• Know as soon as your favourite artists drop new albums.
• Get stories about your interests and hobbies.
• Follow interesting topics, straight from Search results.


Search safely and securely:
• All searches in the Google app are protected by encrypting the connection between your device and Google.
• Privacy controls are easy to find and use. Tap your profile picture to access your menu and delete recent search history from your account with one click.
• Search takes a proactive approach to filtering webspam to help ensure that you see safe, high-quality results.


More ways to access Google:
• Google Search widget — search from your home screen or lock screen with the new Google widget. Choose from two widgets, giving you a quick access search bar in both sizes, and other search shortcuts to choose from such as Lens, Voice and Incognito in the medium-sized widget.


Learn more about what the Google app can do for you: http://www.google.com/search/about

Privacy policy: https://www.google.com/policies/privacy

Discover the pinnacle of security and privacy with Mix VPN, an advanced Virtual Private Network solution designed to safeguard your online activities. Mix VPN offers unparalleled features that ensure a secure and confidential connection to the Internet, setting a new standard in digital protection.



Mix VPN is a robust implementation of Virtual Private Network technology, offering a secure and private Internet connection.



Key Features of Mix VPN:



1. Strict no-logs policy:



Mix VPN ensures your browsing history and personal data are never logged or collected.



2. Multi-hop function:



Utilize sequences of servers to enhance your anonymity and security online. Our AI-based server selection feature intelligently chooses servers based on real-time channel conditions specific to your current location.



3. Kill-Switch:



Kill-switch feature automatically blocks internet traffic if the VPN connection drops, ensuring your data remains protected.



4. Impressive speed:



Benefit from high connection speeds across our VPN servers.



5. State-of-the-art encryption:



We employ the IKEv2 protocol to maximize your online data security.



6. Global server network:



Connect to servers in over 10 countries worldwide with Mix VPN.



7. User-friendly interface:



Enjoy advanced protection with an intuitive setup that's accessible to everyone.



8. 24/7 customer support:



Our team is available round-the-clock to assist you with any inquiries.



Mix VPN acts as your trusted online shield, safeguarding privacy and granting access to Internet resources while protecting you from threats like hacking, fraud, and unwanted data surveillance.

Trusted by millions worldwide, Proton VPN is the world's only free VPN app that is safe to use and respects your privacy.

Proton VPN was created by the CERN scientists behind Proton Mail - the world's largest encrypted email service.

• Full disk encrypted servers protect your data
• Perfect forward secrecy: encrypted traffic cannot be captured and decrypted later
• DNS leak protection: we encrypt DNS queries to ensure that your browsing activity cannot be exposed through DNS leaks
• Always-on VPN/ kill switch offers protection against leaks caused by accidental disconnections

Premium VPN features:
• Access 15000+ high speed servers across 120+ countries worldwide including US, UK, France, Germany, India, Brazil, Mexico, Japan, South Korea, etc.

• Stream films, sports events, and videos on any streaming service (Netflix, Hulu, Amazon Prime Video, Disney+, Max, BBC iPlayer etc)
• File-sharing and P2P support
• Secure Core servers protect against network-based attacks with multi-hop VPN
• Tor over VPN provides automatic integration with the Tor anonymity network

Why Proton VPN?
• No personal data required to sign up
• Easy-to-use VPN app for iPhone, iPad, visionOS, tvOS, Mac, and any other major devices
• Highest strength encryption for your connection makes it better than an internet proxy
• One tap Connect to secure your internet connection, especially on public Wifi hotspots
• Unique VPN Accelerator technology increases your VPN speed by up to 400% for a faster internet connection
• Proton VPN's Secure Core architecture allows our secure VPN service to defend against network-based attacks
• We only use VPN protocols that are proven to be secure: WireGuard
• Independently audited by third-party security experts and we publish all results on our website
• Trusted open-source code that can be reviewed for security by anyone
• Data protection using AES-256 and 4096 RSA encryption

Join the privacy revolution
• Your support is important as it allows us to continue our mission to bring online freedom to people around the globe. Get our private VPN free today and enjoy fast VPN connections and a secure internet, from anywhere.

Global VPN server network

It is the 21st century, and everything is becoming digital: books, games, meetings. Why? It is more convenient and comfortable. That is why we want to introduce our new app - the Smart Remote app for TCL and Roku TV.

Smart Remote app transforms your phone into a remote control center for the Roku, TCL, Hisense or Insignia TV. It is easy to understand with our intuitive display, and right after install you can begin to control your Smart TV, Roku TV, Streaming Stick, Express, Player or Box.

Did we tell you that our app offers your remote Mirroring Screen for TCL, Roku or Smart TV?

If you have eyesight problems and always need to put your glasses on or go near a TV, forget it!

Now you can just look at your smartphone and see everything you need. Not only Screen Mirroring, but also you can make a TV cast of your favorite videos.

We all know the eternal problem of remotes is getting lost. One of the best things is that you won’t lose a phone at the apartment, or at least you can call your phone to find it. Now you won’t need an old Hisense or Insignia remote because you have one on your phone. It acts as a TCL TV remote, and it doesn’t need batteries. It perfectly and automatically connects with Roku as well.

For you, nothing will change, except now you always know where your TV remote control is. Just connect it through your Wi-Fi, and it is ready to go. New TLC, Roku, Hisense or Insignia remote will have the same functionality and even more:
· Power On / Off
· Volume Up / Down Control
· Roku Channels Control
· Navigation Buttons Up / Down / Left / Right
· You still can use play, pause, fast forward, and rewind while the player is active
· You always know where your TV remote is
· It works with Roku and Hisense as well as a familiar remote control
· You can use the Screen Mirroring function if something is not visible clearly or enjoy streaming videos or photos from your phone on a bigger screen with a TV cast function.

So don’t waste your time finding your remote or buying new batteries. Just downloading the Smart Remote app transforms your phone into the remote control for the TCL, Roku, Insignia, Hisense, or other TV. Easy to use, everything an old Insignia TV remote had, now in your smartphone, is your new Insignia. It will automatically connect to your Smart TV, so you don’t need to do it every time. You can use TV to cast it.

Revolutionize Your Entertainment with Screen Mirroring | Cast to TV

Stay connected and stream effortlessly with Screen Mirroring | Cast to TV. The app lets you mirror your screen or cast your phone to devices like Roku, LG, Chromecast, Fire TV, Samsung Smart TVs, and more. Compatible with iPhone mirroring, AirPlay, Miracast, and Smart View, it delivers seamless streaming and sharp, high-definition quality across all platforms.

How to Connect iPhone to TV:
1. Open the app and tap the Connect TV button on the home screen.
2. When prompted, tap Allow in the local network access request window.
3. Ensure both your phone and smart TV are connected to the same Wi-Fi network and VPN services are disabled.
4. Wait for your smart TV to appear in the list of devices.
5. Select your TV and wait for the connection to establish.
6. If additional steps are required on your TV, follow the on-screen instructions on your phone (e.g., confirm the connection on the TV using Yes or Allow).

Powerful Features for Every Need
- Full Screen Mirroring
Mirror your entire screen for gaming, presentations, or enhanced browsing on a larger display with seamless functionality.
- Cast Web Videos and Cast YouTube
Stream videos from YouTube or the web effortlessly using our new web video cast and web casting tools. Enjoy high-quality playback straight on your TV!
- Photo and Video Casting
Showcase your photo gallery and favorite videos on the big screen with photo mirroring, perfect for reliving memories with loved ones and having a cinema-like experience at home.
- IPTV
Stream a variety of channels through live television. With the best online TV streaming, finding live TV streaming options is as simple as ever. Get access to IPTV!
- Universal Compatibility
Supports a wide range of smart TVs and streaming devices, including Samsung, Roku, LG, Chromecast, Fire TV, and Vizio, for ultimate flexibility.
- User-Friendly Setup
Featuring an intuitive interface with quick-connect options, you can immediately connect to your TV—no complex configurations needed!
- High-Quality Performance
Lag-free streaming and crystal-clear visuals ensure you enjoy an unparalleled experience, whether you're casting YouTube on TV or using other features.
- AI Movie Advisor
Get a personalized list of movies and series tailored to your taste. Finding the perfect movies to watch has never been easier!
- Live Camera
Perfect for turning your device into a video nanny, streaming live presentations, capturing family gatherings, or sharing lessons and sessions in real-time.

*This app provides access to third-party IPTV streams, which are not controlled or modified by the developer. Content availability may vary, and the developer is not responsible for the nature, accuracy, or legality of streamed content. Viewer discretion is advised.

Why Choose Screen Mirroring | Cast to TV?
This app blends simplicity with cutting-edge streaming, perfect for sharing photos, binge-watching, or presentations. With versatile tools like a web/video caster and reliable cross-platform compatibility, it ensures seamless streaming for any modern home setup.

Elevate Your Streaming Experience
Unlock the full potential of your devices with Screen Mirroring | Cast to TV. Whether you're using AirPlay, Miracast, Smart View, DLNA, Chromecast, or exploring web video casting features, this app simplifies how you connect and stream. Take control of your entertainment with an app that delivers on every promise, from casting YouTube on TV to mirroring your entire device.

Take control of your internet with Firefox.
When you choose Firefox, you’re choosing to stay private, stay focused, and stay in charge.

PRIVACY WHERE IT MATTERS MOST
Firefox blocks hidden trackers that follow you around the internet and slow down your browsing. Want more control? Switch Enhanced Tracking Protection to Strict mode for extra protection across all your tabs. Or browse in a private window — your search and browsing history disappears when all your private tabs are closed.

DIFFERENT DEVICES. SAME TRAIN OF THOUGHT
Start a search on your phone and pick it up on your laptop — or vice versa. With a Mozilla account, your open tabs, history, and bookmarks travel with you. Firefox can even suggest strong passwords when you’re creating a new account and securely store them so they’re available across all your devices.

STREAMLINED HOME SCREEN
Pick up right where you left off. Your open tabs are intuitively grouped and displayed, along with recent bookmarks, top sites, and popular articles.

FIND IT FAST WITH FIREFOX’S SEARCH BAR
Get search suggestions in the search bar and quickly access the sites you visit most. Type in your search query and get suggested and previously searched results across your preferred search engines.

ORGANISE YOUR TABS THE WAY YOU LIKE
Open as many tabs as you like without losing track. Firefox displays your open tabs as thumbnails, making it easy to quickly find what you want.

SHARE ANYTHING IN A FEW TAPS
Easily share links to web pages or specific items on a page, with quick access to your most recently used apps.

BILLIONAIRE-FREE FOR OVER 20 YEARS
The Firefox browser was created in 2004 by Mozilla as a faster, more private, and more customisable alternative to other web browsers. Today, we’re still not-for-profit, still not owned by any billionaires, and still working to make the internet — and the time you spend on it — better. To learn more about Mozilla, visit https://www.mozilla.org.

LEARN MORE

– Privacy Policy: https://www.mozilla.org/privacy/firefox
